{"tid":337537,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"開始有公司讓員工植入晶片，方便返工！","createTime":"2017-07-27T11:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T13:57:50.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"903cd073c6ec24ee38be190ad09eac1a2b7e0d3a","tid":337537,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T11:35:49.000Z","msg":"位於美國威斯康辛州的自助售賣技術公司Three Square Market（32M）公司近日宣布，將會讓所有員工可以選擇在手上植入晶片，方便工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://image1.thenewslens.com/2017/7/t9bj320jfc1ovixejw8n0iz6lf6hm1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage1.thenewslens.com%2F2017%2F7%2Ft9bj320jfc1ovixejw8n0iz6lf6hm1.jpg&h=6fbdeea7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n晶片採用的無線射頻辨識（RFID）技術，32M指晶片可以讓員工在公司的休息室買東西、開門、登入電腦、使用影印機等&mdash;&mdash;簡單來說，就是不用再怕忘記帶（含智能晶片的）員工證及鎖匙卡，亦不怕忘記密碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n價值300美元（約2342港元）的晶片將會植入皮下，位置在拇指和和食指之間。對於這項技術有興趣，但不想把晶片植入體內的員工，32M亦提供另一選擇，把晶片放入手帶或智能戒指。<br />\n<br />\n32M強調，晶片沒有全球定位系統（GPS）技術，無法用來追蹤員工位置，而RFID閱讀器須在數吋範圍內才可以讀取晶片上的資訊。晶片內的數據亦經過加密，就如採用相同技術的信用卡一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/74555\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F74555&d=ALUAnwbwHc4NfDmR6FIHkXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=d212ffbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/74555</a>"},{"pid":"6ba6e2559155e9d23a2f542c6ad45cdbb27be1d8","tid":337537,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T10:59:23.000Z","msg":"如果比支那政府抄到一定會變質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce9d2cd9586536a4688d1d830b81b3ea75f02fc","tid":337537,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:03:45.000Z","msg":"奴隸獸，奴隸獸"},{"pid":"836a30dad07c3b498a39758ab37364df80736e1f","tid":337537,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"